Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼醜的女人\N還是有一點可取之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.15,0:02:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛！幹什麼\N我都讚美你了你還這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.79,0:02:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥你這性格再不改的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定沒有女孩會喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.56,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉唆！你一定沒有人要娶你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.83,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼去準備午飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心今天的菜是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是。。牛膀。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了昨天醃的茄子也可以吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.62,0:03:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拮据\N偶爾也該去吃一吃好吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寄居在這裏還敢說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.62,0:03:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想想看我們哪裏有錢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊。在這麼窮的道場裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼翻來覆去也只有灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！走開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪呢…我記得在這附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在做什麼呢？阿熏這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是頭殼被打壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個這個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺所畫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便亂畫的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是水墨畫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.10,0:04:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼好的筆法確實是阿熏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.54,0:04:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爺爺是劍術家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時也是水墨畫家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個賣了就有錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊。。謝謝爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.25,0:04:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼！中午我們去牛肉火鍋店\N大吃一頓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一起去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了！不愧是阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有好的地方太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本第一！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是會逢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.00,0:04:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇。。牛肉火鍋牛肉火鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.38,0:04:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥別狼吞虎嚥\N吃得太急的話對身體不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.49,0:04:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看吧，真的需要人照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥也需要阿熏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.30,0:05:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種做法，自由民權的社會\N沒辦法來臨的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該再激烈一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.17,0:05:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那樣跟把板坦老師\N逼入死地是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊!內務聊的大久保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.01,0:05:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比大西鄉還不能容赦的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果死了能成星星的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.85,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼老師也會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說這種笨話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於這種浪漫的比喻\N又有什麼用處呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀！板垣老師若死了\N那自由會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.75,0:05:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是自由民權運動的壯士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.79,0:05:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的政府\N一部份的人掌握實權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了要改變這狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.67,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓更多的人參加政治的運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這好像是一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是看到那些人後就有一點。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼看也只像是喝醉酒一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像禰彥所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.46,0:06:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼！再說一遍看看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的自由民權運動\N說幾次也沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是木頭人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用碗丟人\N你們還在那裏議論什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.45,0:06:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事等一下再說！先來道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉唆！你這小鬼對我們這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.42,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由民權的壯士\N有意見還早一百年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是什麼小鬼\N我叫你們道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些醉鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼醉鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是自由民權者！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.36,0:06:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉唆！醉了的話\N不論誰都是醉鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.04,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,客人。。在這裏爭吵\N不太好。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.77,0:06:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口！女人不要加進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿妙姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.15,0:07:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂！自由民權\N是為弱者而存在的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.35,0:07:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是你們所說的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由民權是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醉了後自由的使用暴力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.80,0:07:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.00,0:07:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是。。是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想找碴吵架嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊偶像找碴吵架也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般我是招惹人的專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.44,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不喜歡欺侮弱者\N也不喜歡看人欺侮弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.82,0:07:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別對那些高喊自由\N正義平等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.02,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的偽善混蛋的欺侮人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更是非常的生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.09,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！！你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到外面去！外面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像變得很奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止他們比較好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己想要這麼做的，隨便他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哭了我也不會饒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先試試你的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打一拳試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙！有隱藏著寸鐵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要叫嚷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寸鐵本來就是隱藏的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.55,0:08:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如那些傢伙所說的。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點用處都沒有。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用寸鐵了還這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊。。我的手我的手！
