Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果打算拔刀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生也不會原諒你的
