Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是對於你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該於政府修正之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先自己要行得正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,付完錢後快給我滾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.06,0:09:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.33,0:10:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼，我只是喜歡打架\N不需要道謝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造成這些騷動真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼劍客先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你頭上的傷不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.94,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩？啊。。沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是，你故意不躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果受傷了\N不就太裝模作樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.08,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.58,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候如果你躲開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐的臉現在就會都是血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.02,0:10:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你不躲開\N而以自己的頭當盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把我看得太高了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用謙虛了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.63,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜歡你，要跟我打架嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我謝絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.81,0:10:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果改變主意隨時來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我住在村外的流氓屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那人是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是好人還是壞人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是怪興趣的壞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇怪的男人。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道他嗎？阿妙姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.24,0:11:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人還沒有付錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白吃白喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.98,0:11:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是傳說中\N專門打架的斬左。。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.75,0:11:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果利用那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.78,0:11:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那討厭的男人一定會被打倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.86,0:11:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？幫我收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是認為\N我是專門殺人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.01,0:11:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要想錯了好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.17,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會死\N也要看那傢伙的運氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.51,0:12:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只要快樂的打架就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.88,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想是可以\N讓你十二分快樂的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向你保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.79,0:12:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我來看\N你大約也是派來的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.40,0:12:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有特地來拜託替人打架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是斬左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.77,0:12:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼那個劍心\N到底是個怎樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活在地道裏的蛇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.71,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是指活在世界上的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說也要知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.92,0:12:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫劍心的男人\N事實上是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎？喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.13,0:12:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣斬左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手對你來說沒有不滿意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.34,0:12:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這也是你揚名的好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟這沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.52,0:13:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒遇到旗鼓相當的對手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的殺人王緋村拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我專門打架的斬左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是在找這種猛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.33,0:13:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,專門打架的斬左在黑暗世界\N名震天下的打架代行人。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.63,0:14:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打架是以自己的樂趣來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡傲慢的一匹狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.84,0:14:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是很強\N終於可以戰鬥的人。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.25,0:14:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背後的惡文字連夢裏也會看到\N可以說是夢魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.05,0:14:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著瞧。緋村拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.11,0:14:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他而使我不能再握劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.11,0:14:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個仇恨\N我一輩子也不會忘記的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.70,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行已經這麼晚了\N還在這裏打攪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄齋大夫再等一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小綾和小雀都睡得很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下我送你們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.28,0:15:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！禰彥偶爾也會說些好話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾可以省略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有客人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.03,0:15:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.86,0:15:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等。。等一下，劍心怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒想要隱藏的正直的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬥氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來打架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那人！是白天的。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一招見勝負的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.49,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說我拒絕打架嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是專門打架的打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不可能退下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且對手又是維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人拔刀齋就更要打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會知道那些呢。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.78,0:16:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長州派維新志士緋村拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.95,0:16:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一個名字叫殺人拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.29,0:16:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所使用的是\N古流派飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查的很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是專門打架的人\N的工作之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些根本不用去調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還有不知道的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.54,0:16:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流是什麼樣的劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺無情的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是成為\N不殺人的流浪漢的原委
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.15,0:17:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.95,0:17:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要堂堂正正的分出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不喜歡欺侮弱者的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又為什麼專門打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做這麼不合理的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.55,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼原因讓你變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.82,0:17:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.43,0:17:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想會會你這傳說中的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.47,0:17:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想打倒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起我還沒自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字叫相樂左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬馬刀的左之助簡稱斬左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.19,0:18:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.27,0:18:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬馬刀的左之助簡稱斬左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬馬刀？！那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是以前敵將用來砍倒馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所製造的最大的刀劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為太重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.54,0:18:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一個人能完美使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要認為我不會殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快！拿那麼重大的武器\N還這麼快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看清了你的動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次不會讓你逃掉了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥你在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小綾小雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.73,0:20:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的打架\N是不該讓小女孩看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.17,0:20:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且那好像是有點髒的殺氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.71,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.48,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有誰在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是拔刀齋。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.52,0:20:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我先說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你即使沒那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.19,0:20:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被我這專門打架的人看上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對是跑不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那樣的恨維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.51,0:20:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個架好像是避不了的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.58,0:20:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.99,0:20:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼小綾小雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.66,0:21:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生跟禰彥送你們回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.93,0:21:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇。。哇。。

